        &lt;h1 class="g2 fiu d4"&gt;Workflow Into Orbit&lt;/h1&gt;
        &lt;p class="sub fiu d6"&gt;Supercharge productivity with AI-powered
          automation built for the next generation of teams.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;div class="btns fiu d8"&gt;
          &lt;a href="#" class="bp"&gt;Get Started for Free&lt;/a&gt;
